Map Legend & Info

This map is an interactable demo that shows news articles per location from a sample of the 2022-2023 Dutch NewsCrawl subset.

Clusters: Colours are related to cluster intensity of location mentions.

Markers: The markers show locations and their related news articles .

Popup: Click a marker to see articles corresponding to that location.

Search: You can search by location name using the bar on top.

All samples are limited to areas near the coordinates of the Netherlands and are selected based on high-confidence matches—entities exhibiting strong linguistic similarity to real-world locations—to ensure data validity.
